snippet.title: Game Progression I Feature Highlights Ep 10 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
20 milestones packed with rewards & a whole new system of development trees!  
🎁Learn how you can unlock milestones in Cities: Skylines II, how you can respond to your city's growing needs & how to use development points to build the city of your dreams.🏗️

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.

Pre-Order Cities: Skylines II NOW!
